properties.areaDesc: Delaware Bay waters south of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE; Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE
properties.headline: Storm Warning issued February 6 at 8:13PM EST until February 7 at 6:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 25 to 35 kt with gusts up to 50 kt and
extremely rough waters expected.

* WHERE...Delaware Bay.

* WHEN...From 6 AM to 6 PM EST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Very strong winds will cause hazardous seas which
could capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Winds are likely to increase rapidly by
mid-morning on Friday. Very hazardous conditions are expected on
the waters during the day.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should remain in port, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: STORM WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 6 AM TO 6 PM EST FRIDAY
